title: Arbor Snowboards :: Product Profiles - Wasteland
description:
Arbor’s flagship - designed around our most current thinking on big mountain design, our award winning System set of rocker technologies, and an inlaid version of our power ply topsheet in order to deliver cutting edge performance and versatility. Go anywhere, in or out of bounds, and ride with the confidence that only the Wasteland provides.
To learn more about the Wasteland visit: arborcollective.com/snowboards/products/wasteland/
